(3825, 2, '2016-03-19 13:38:24', '2016-03-19 13:38:24', '[vc_row bg_type="bg_color" bg_override="full" bg_color_value="#ececec"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="The Sage Promise" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%23666666" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1460531360999{padding-top: 20px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1463567097926{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We promise to only recommend hearing devices with proven success and excellent value.  Doing so at prices that are affordable to every budget.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="<strong>Sage Hearing Solutions</strong> Provides Your On-going Hearing Needs into the Future" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center" use_theme_fonts="yes"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1463567520800{padding-right: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; text-align: justify;">Sage Hearing Solutions is the local leading provider of premium products and services for individuals with hearing loss in Beaverton and surrounding areas. We do this by offering state of the art testing, diagnostics, and care.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; text-align: justify;">At Sage, our patient’s satisfaction is the cornerstone of our business. That’s why we take our time in working with each person. By considering your needs, lifestyle, and budget, we will find a solution that helps you get the most out of life. We pride ourselves on offering the best care possible, and are here to help guide you every step of the way.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="4070" img_size="large" alignment="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;">We provide an array of screenings, hearing tests and aural rehabilitation.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-wrench" icon_size="22" icon_color="#662f6c" title="How to use your hearing aids" pos="right" title_font_size="16" title_font_color="#666666"][/bsf-info-box][bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-check" icon_size="22" icon_color="#662f6c" title="State-of-the-art technology" pos="right" title_font_size="16" title_font_color="#666666"][/bsf-info-box][bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-cog gear" icon_size="22" icon_color="#662f6c" title="Conventional and digital instruments" pos="right" title_font_size="16" title_font_color="#666666"][/bsf-info-box][bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-star" icon_size="22" icon_color="#662f6c" title="Commitment to your health and well being" pos="right" title_font_size="16" title_font_color="#666666"][/bsf-info-box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-asterisk" icon_size="22" icon_color="#662f6c" title="Honest communication" pos="left" title_font_size="16" title_font_color="#666666"][/bsf-info-box][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" icon_img="4082|http://www.riseforwar.com/xxx-content/uploads/2016/03/wind.png" img_width="22" title="No feeling of being rushed or pressured" pos="left" title_font_size="16" title_font_color="#666666"][/bsf-info-box]\r\n\r\n[bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-smile-o" icon_size="22" icon_color="#662f6c" title="Complete satisfaction is guaranteed" pos="left" title_font_size="16" title_font_color="#666666"][/bsf-info-box]\r\n\r\n[bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-book" icon_size="22" icon_color="#662f6c" title="Patient and family education about the strategies of hearing improvement" pos="left" title_font_size="16" title_font_color="#666666"][/bsf-info-box][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Who We Are', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'who-we-are', '', '', '2016-05-20 08:59:25', '2016-05-20 08:59:25', '', 0, 'http://www.riseforwar.com/?page_id=3825', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3826, 2, '2016-03-19 13:38:40', '2016-03-19 13:38:40', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">David King is a Hearing Care Specialist that has served patients in Oregon and Arizona for over 13 years.  He currently lives in Beaverton with his wife, Jaimie, and their two young children, Parker and Haley.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The cornerstone of David''s professionalism is built on his commitment to serving the hearing impaired and to exceed the expectations of his patients.  After working for over a decade with a National Audiology Company, he and his wife decided to open their own practice to better serve the needs of their community.  By combining integrity and knowledge he naturally demonstrates a unique ability to educate his patients and their families about the strategies and care of hearing impairment.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">While using state of the art equipment and technology, David provides an array of screenings, hearing tests, aural rehabilitation and expansive knowledge of both conventional and digital instruments.  With over a decade of experience in the hearing health care field, David''s commitment to excellent patient care is evident in each and every person he works with.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">David understands the importance of taking the time to really listen to his patients.  He creates an environment where open and honest communication can take place and his patients can make decisions about their hearing needs based on facts and years of success, all without the feeling of being rushed or pressured.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">David''s knowledge in communication disorders has helped improve the quality of life for thousands of people in his community.  By starting Sage Hearing Solutions, he now has the ability to offer the same quality service at more affordable prices to those in need of Hearing Health Care.  You can depend on David to provide the absolute best solution for you.  We are confident that you will be satisfied with his skills and desire to not only meet your expectations, but also far exceed them.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_empty_space height="80px"][vc_single_image image="3959" img_size="full" alignment="center" style="vc_box_outline_circle_2"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Our Professionals', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-professionals', '', '', '2016-05-18 10:47:02', '2016-05-18 10:47:02', '', 0, 'http://www.riseforwar.com/?page_id=3826', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3827, 2, '2016-03-19 13:38:49', '2016-03-19 13:38:49', '[vc_row][vc_column][porto_history animation_delay="1000" year="2014" image="4123" animation_type="bounceInRight" label=""]Sage Hearing Solutions is born to help hearing impaired patients get the most out of life.[/porto_history][porto_history animation_delay="1000" year="2012" image="4108" animation_type="bounceInLeft"]David moves to Scottsdale, AZ and holds a Regional Management Position for a National Hearing Aid Company.[/porto_history][porto_history year="2004" image="4110" animation_type="bounceIn"]David serves patients in Portland, Oregon’s West Side[/porto_history][porto_history year="2001" image="4111" animation_type="bounceIn"]David begins serving patients in Oregon’s East Side[/porto_history][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Our History', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-history', '', '', '2016-05-26 06:11:06', '2016-05-26 06:11:06', '', 0, 'http://www.riseforwar.com/?page_id=3827', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3828, 2, '2016-03-19 13:40:10', '2016-03-19 13:40:10', '[vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column width="1/2"][porto_testimonial style="testimonial-style-3" name="Rebecca Blair" company="Beaverton OR" photo_id="4007"]On Saturday morning of the 2015 Labor Day weekend, the tubing on my father''s right hearing aid broke.  I called six different hearing aid businesses in the Beaverton/Portland area and got six different answering machine recordings.  Five of those recordings said they would return my call on Tuesday when their offices reopened.  Only David at Sage Hearing identified himself by name on his recording in which he promised a return call by the end of the day.  He called after just two hours and offered to wait the 30 minutes it would take for us to get to his office (on his holiday weekend!) simply saying, "We are here to serve the community."  When we arrived, David took the time to gather my father''s hearing history and proceeded to remove and replace the broken tubing.  He tested both of my father''s hearing aids, made sure they fit properly and were working correctly before we left his office.  My father was thrilled with the results and so was I.  I would highly recommend the professionalism and experience of David King at Sage Hearing Solutions to anyone.[/porto_testimonial][porto_testimonial style="testimonial-style-3" name="Kurt Trade" company="National Account Manager /Trainer" photo_id="4007" label=""]I have worked with David King for many years now as the National Account Manager / Trainer for Oticon, Inc. and found him to be highly motivated to deliver high quality advice to his patients. David has shown me that his concern for the well-being of his patients is paramount in his approach to providing hearing healthcare to them. As well, he continually looks to enhance his audiological and consultative knowledge to provide enhanced treatment to those he consults in his practice. I would recommend him to my family and friends when they were in need of amplification.[/porto_testimonial][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][porto_testimonial style="testimonial-style-3" name="Dennis Eckel" company="Scottsdale AZ" photo_id="4007"]After years of procrastination, I finally found someone I could trust to give me straight answers about my hearing. I am now able to hear sounds that had escaped me for years, thanks to David.  David tested and identified the regions where my hearing was impaired. He offered an open and honest conversation about what could be done to improve my hearing loss and what I could expect from a hearing device. He then suggested best-value options for my lifestyle. Once purchased, he continued to test and reprogram the device to maximize its effectiveness. He provided care and maintenance tips and helped make the device comfortable to wear. David was always patient and professional. I also know David and his family personally. He is a loving husband and father and he is involved in his community.[/porto_testimonial][porto_testimonial style="testimonial-style-3" name="Lee Vinyard" company="Scottsdale , AZ" photo_id="4007"]In June of 2012, I was introduced to a new practitioner, David. The consultation resulted in my having a professional with superb knowledge of his field and qualified to attend to all of my hearing concerns. He made significant improvements in my hearing with thorough examinations, and properly fitted devices. He took ample time to explain the products, their costs, and their importance. Without question, I highly recommend David to future clients!![/porto_testimonial][porto_testimonial style="testimonial-style-3" name="Charlene T" company="Beaverton OR" photo_id="4007"]No one in my office knows I have hearing aids and to be able to bring the quality of life back to what it once was is priceless. I can never thank David and his staff enough for taking the time to explain everything about hearing loss, to help me see what I was missing. I encourage anyone with a hearing loss to see David. I have never been happier, the sounds I had been missing still bring tears to my eyes, as I''m glad I did go and get this taken care of.[/porto_testimonial][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Testimonials', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'testimonials', '', '', '2016-03-26 12:43:55', '2016-03-26 12:43:55', '', 0, 'http://www.riseforwar.com/?page_id=3828', 0, 'page', '', 0),
