(3847, 2, '2016-03-19 14:00:22', '2016-03-19 14:00:22', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image="3988" img_size="medium" alignment="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][porto_content_box][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="OPN" pos="top"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Opn is Oticon’s newest and most advanced hearing aid to date. It represents a leap forward in hearing care by combining breakthrough technologies that enables users to hear better with less listening effort. By employing an ‘open sound’ approach, users can now focus on a conversation while staying attentive to people and things around them. Opn is available in a wide range of styles and options.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][porto_content_box skin="primary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="ALTA 2" pos="top" title_font_color="#0088cc"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Alta2’s BrainHearing™ technology gives your brain what it needs to make sense of sound for a more natural, effortless hearing experience. What makes Alta2 performance so effective is that it can be personalized, with more detail and automation than ever, to fit your unique hearing profile and lifestyle. Alta2 is available in a wide range of styles and options.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/3"][porto_content_box skin="secondary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="NERA2" pos="top" title_font_color="#e36159"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nera2 is Oticon’s most advanced mid-level hearing device ever. It works smarter, so you don’t have to work as hard at hearing — and you can maintain your active lifestyle throughout the day. Nera2 is available in a wide range of styles and options.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][porto_content_box skin="tertiary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="RIA2" pos="top" title_font_color="#2baab1"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ria2 provides all the essentials you need for better hearing – at an affordable price. You can now interact more naturally and comfortably with your environment throughout the day. Ria2 is available in a wide range of styles and options.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][porto_content_box skin="quaternary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="DYNAMO" pos="top" title_font_color="#383f48"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Dynamo is Oticon''s most innovative super power hearing instrument to date. It is a powerful advance in hearing technology for meeting the challenges of severe-to-profound hearing loss. In Dynamo, Oticon’s Brain Hearing™ technology makes spoken sound more understandable; preserves the clarity of speech; and delivers sound in the way your brain, with its unique hearing profile, is best able to understand it.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_type="bg_color" bg_override="full"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="Connectline and Streamer pro" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%23666666" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1460444166907{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1463570312037{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]ConnectLine makes it easy and convenient to use Oticon hearing instruments as a personal wireless headset, enabling better connections with people, information and entertainment.[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="Features and Functions" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:center|color:%23666666" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1458829050983{padding-bottom: 5px !important;}"][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1458812218202{background-color: fcfcfc !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-rss" icon_size="28" icon_color="#662d6c" hover_effect="style_2" pos="top"]\r\n<p style="font-size: 16px; text-align: center;">Wireless connections to TV, landlines, cellphones and more</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-volume-up" icon_size="28" icon_color="#662d6c" hover_effect="style_2" pos="top"]\r\n<p style="font-size: 16px;">Easy to select streaming sources</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][bsf-info-box icon="Simple-Line-Icons-earphones" icon_size="28" icon_color="#662d6c" hover_effect="style_2" pos="top"]\r\n<p style="font-size: 16px;">Discreet remote control for hearing instruments</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_type="bg_color" bg_override="full"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="ConnectLine Devices" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:center|color:%23666666" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1460444196960{padding-bottom: 5px !important;}"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-wifi" icon_size="28" icon_color="#662d6c" title="Streamer Pro" hover_effect="style_2" pos="top"]\r\n<p style="font-size: 16px;">The gateway to wireless connections</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-file-movie-o file-video-o" icon_size="28" icon_color="#662d6c" title="TV Adapter" hover_effect="style_2" pos="top"]\r\n<p style="font-size: 16px;">For comfortable TV viewing</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-microphone" icon_size="28" icon_color="#662d6c" title="Microphone" hover_effect="style_2" pos="top"]For one-on-one conversations[/bsf-info-box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][bsf-info-box icon="Defaults-phone" icon_size="28" icon_color="#662d6c" title="Phone Adapter" hover_effect="style_2" pos="top"]Simple connections to landline phones[/bsf-info-box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Oticon', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'oticon', '', '', '2016-05-18 12:35:44', '2016-05-18 12:35:44', '', 0, 'http://www.riseforwar.com/?page_id=3847', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3848, 2, '2016-03-19 13:59:15', '2016-03-19 13:59:15', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image="4044" img_size="medium" add_caption="yes" alignment="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box  box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" icon_img="4114|http://www.riseforwar.com/xxx-content/uploads/2016/05/rsz_signia-pure-binax.jpg" img_width="120" title="<center>Signia Primax</center>" pos="top" title_font_color="#662f6c"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Signia (formerly known as Siemens) Primax is the company’s most advanced hearing aid platform to date. It is the world’s first technology clinically proven by independent studies to reduce listening effort throughout the day while providing better than normal hearing in challenging listening environments.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="secondary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" icon_img="3929|http://www.riseforwar.com/xxx-content/uploads/2016/03/ace.png" img_width="120" title="\r\n\r\n<center>Ace Binax</center>" pos="top" title_font_color="#e36159"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Ace Binax is Siemens’ tiniest RIC hearing aid and offers utmost discretion and a superb listening experience. It is an optimum solution for first-time wearers or people that demand discretion and convenience. With Ace Binax, you no longer have to choose between discretion and functionality – you can have both. Despite it’s tiny size, it is packed with some amazing features including resistance to water, sweat, dust and dirt.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="tertiary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" icon_img="3930|http://www.riseforwar.com/xxx-content/uploads/2016/03/pure.png" img_width="120" title="\r\n\r\n<center>Pure Binax</center>" pos="top" title_font_color="#2baab1"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Pure Binax offers an outstanding binaural hearing experience, sophisticated features, and elegant design. The receiver sits directly in your ear canal and fits moderate to severe hearing loss. Despite it’s tiny size, it is packed with features and is among the industry’s lowest battery consumption. So you can enjoy the best listening experience all the time without concerns about battery life.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="quaternary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" icon_img="3931|http://www.riseforwar.com/xxx-content/uploads/2016/03/carat.png" img_width="120" title="\r\n\r\n<center>Carat Binax</center>" pos="top" title_font_color="#383f48"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Carat Binax is discreet, compact and easy-to-handle. It provides an exceptional binaural listening experience and with longer battery life. Carat’s design is balanced and compact, equipped with many advanced features. Thanks to the latest BestSound™ Technology — the Carat helps users hear speech in noisy environments and in wind.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="quaternary"  box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" icon_img="3928|http://www.riseforwar.com/xxx-content/uploads/2016/03/aqua.png" img_width="120" title="\r\n\r\n<center>Aquaris</center>" pos="top" title_font_color="#383f48"]\r\n<p style="text-align: Justify;">The Aquaris is the only truly waterproof, dust-proof, and shockproof hearing aid available. Aquaris is perfect for people who spend time in demanding environments due to it’s resistance to dust, perspiration, and humidity. Aquaris is remarkably sturdy, resistant to moisture and dirt, and built to withstand rough-and-tumble activities.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="tertiary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" icon_img="3932|http://www.riseforwar.com/xxx-content/uploads/2016/03/insio.png" img_width="120" title="\r\n\r\n<center>Insio Binax</center>" pos="top" title_font_color="#2baab1"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Insio Binax is a custom hearing solution that offers clear and natural sound without that muffled effect. Insio automatically adjusts to your personal hearing preferences and programs for different hearing situations and offers exceptional sound quality and speech understanding. Insio also features wireless connectivity for direct connection to a wide variety of sound sources.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="secondary" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" icon_img="3933|http://www.riseforwar.com/xxx-content/uploads/2016/03/nitro.png" img_width="120" title="\r\n\r\n<center>Nitro BTE</center>" pos="top" title_font_color="#e36159"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Siemens Nitro® BTE is the ideal solution for people with severe-to-profound hearing loss who want to stay involved and active. These super power hearing aids not only provide the necessary amplification, but are also powered by Siemens’ BestSound™ Technology.  Siemens Nitro hearing aids give you the sound experience you desire, all with remarkably low battery consumption. To top it off, nearly all Nitro models offer wireless connectivity.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Siemens', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'siemens', '', '', '2016-05-24 08:50:13', '2016-05-24 08:50:13', '', 0, 'http://www.riseforwar.com/?page_id=3848', 0, 'page', '', 0),
