(3853, 2, '2016-03-19 14:01:03', '2016-03-19 14:01:03', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image="3989" img_size="medium" alignment="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="primary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="AUDEO V" pos="top" title_font_color="#0088cc"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Audeo V is Phonak’s most advanced hearing aid that automatically adjusts to your specific listening environment. It focuses on speech understanding, comfort and ease-of-use, and is tailored to give you the listening experience you desire. Since you move between many listening situations daily, the Audeo V’s sophisticated operating system will adapt to your precise environment and deliver unmatched sound quality with minimal interaction. The AudeoV comes in a variety of price points and styles.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="secondary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="Bolero V" pos="top" title_font_color="#e36159"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Bolero V brings you Phonak’s latest high-performance technology packed into a robust and beautiful design. It has been developed to automatically adapt to your sound environment and gives you the freedom to seamlessly move between listening situations. So not matter how challenging of an environment you’re in, the Bolero V has you covered. The Bolero V comes in a variety of price points and styles.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="tertiary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="VIRTO V" pos="top" title_font_color="#2baab1"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Virto V is Phonak’s custom product family. They are crafted and tailored to perfectly fit into your ear canal while providing ultimate comfort. The Virto V automatically adapts to your specific listening situations, allowing you to better understand speech even in the most challenging environments.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="quaternary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="Lyric " pos="top" title_font_color="#383f48"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Lyric is the world’s only 100% invisible extended-wear hearing device. It can be worn 24/7 for for months-at-a-time and has no batteries to change. The Lyric is placed comfortably in your ear canal by one of our trained hearing professionals with no need for surgery or anesthesia. It is positioned comfortably and completely in the ear canal so it can’t be seen from any angle, at any time. The Lyric can be used during almost all of your daily activities including exercising, showering, sleeping, and talking on the phone.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column]', 'Phonak', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'phonak', '', '', '2016-03-26 12:31:23', '2016-03-26 12:31:23', '', 0, 'http://www.riseforwar.com/?page_id=3853', 0, 'page', '', 0),
