(3902, 2, '2016-03-23 04:43:03', '2016-03-23 04:43:03', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image="3987" img_size="medium" alignment="center"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="secondary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="LiNX<sup>2</sup>" pos="top" title_font_color="#e36159"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The LiNX<sup>2</sup> is the first Made for iPhone<sup>®</sup> hearing aid available on the market. With the LiNX<sup>2</sup>, you can stream phone calls, music, and audio from your Apple<sup>®</sup> products directly to your hearing aids. Direct streaming allows you to completely filter out unnecessary background noise so that you can focus on what you want to hear. The LiNX<sup>2</sup> also features incredibly natural sound quality and a water resistant casing. Modern, discreet and durable, ReSound LiNX2 hearing aids are available in a variety of styles and price points.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="tertiary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="Enya" pos="top" title_font_color="#2baab1"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Enya™ delivers excellent sound quality and speech understanding for all-day listening and wearing comfort. Since every component is coated with water-repellant technology, it has long-lasting protection from water, dust and earwax. With ReSound’s wireless accessories you can stream sound to your hearing aids and have subtle control of your settings. The Enya is available in a variety of styles and price points.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-4 vc_col-xs-12"][porto_content_box skin="quaternary" box_effect="featured-box-effect-1" show_icon="yes"][bsf-info-box icon_type="custom" img_width="48" title="EnZO<sup>2</sup>" pos="top" title_font_color="#383f48"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The EnZO<sup>2</sup> is ReSound’s smart super power hearing aid. With top-rated sound quality, durable design, new personalization options and direct connection to iPhone®, iPad® and iPod Touch® devices - it’s a hearing experience like no other. Not only is it the smartest super power hearing aid available, it’s also the smallest. And it’s protected against moisture, wax and dust with a water-repellent coating.</p>\r\n[/bsf-info-box][/porto_content_box][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_type="bg_color" bg_override="full" bg_color_value="#ececec"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="Unite Wireless Accessories" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%23666666" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1458804702515{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1458804013921{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;">ReSound Unite accessories allow you to stay connected in even more situations, like when watching TV with family,</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;">or when conversing with a friend in noisy surroundings.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="3/4" css=".vc_custom_1458809447966{padding-top: 30px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="ReSound Unite Phone Clip+" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left|color:%23666666" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1458805196711{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1458805246899{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;">The ReSound Unite Phone Clip+ streams crystal clear phone calls and audio straight to your hearing aids. It also works as a hearing aid remote control when you’re not on the phone. For even greater control, use the ReSound Control™ app from your smartphone.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_single_image image="3934" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1458804430481{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_single_image image="3936" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1458808748718{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4" css=".vc_custom_1458809476817{padding-top: 30px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="ReSound Unite Remote Control 2" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left|color:%23666666" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1458808618450{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1458808654422{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;">The ReSound Unite Remote Control 2 allows you to change programs and adjust the volume of your hearing aids easily and discreetly. Now you can change programs and adjust the volume on each of your hearing aids through an easy-to-see display.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="3/4" css=".vc_custom_1458809310608{padding-top: 50px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="ReSound Unite TV Streamer 2" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left|color:%23666666" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1458808233752{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1458808294538{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;">The ReSound Unite TV Streamer 2 sends clear stereo sound from your TV, stereo or computer directly and wirelessly to your hearing aids. Now you can enjoy your favorite programs and music without the hassle of cables or wires.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_single_image image="3935" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1458808379727{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_single_image image="3937" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1458809064685{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}"][/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4" css=".vc_custom_1458809332282{padding-top: 50px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="ReSound Unite Mini Microphone" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left|color:%23666666" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C600%2C600italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C800%2C800italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1458808990723{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1458809021516{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;">The ReSound Unite Mini Microphone offers an extraordinarily versatile device that transmits speech directly to your hearing aids. It is a discreet clip-on microphone that helps you hear speech clearly so you can enjoy one-on-one communication in difficult listening situations.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Resound', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'resound', '', '', '2016-03-26 12:30:11', '2016-03-26 12:30:11', '', 0, 'http://www.riseforwar.com/?page_id=3902', 0, 'page', '', 0),
